statement.title: 题目描述
statement.content: 本题没有输入，请你输出一行 `"Welcome to the SEU Winter Programming Contest!"` (不含引号)

statement.title: 输出格式
statement.content: 仅一行，一个字符串 `"Welcome to the SEU Winter Programming Contest!"` (输出不含引号)

statement.title: 样例
statement.content:
#### 样例输出

``` plain
Welcome to the SEU Winter Programming Contest!
```
